{"tid":498675,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環站幕門故障　港島線列車受阻逾1小時","createTime":"2017-12-14T04:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T14:07:21.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b7149cdb165a670997545d2e2c63df1d294e2269","tid":498675,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171214/photo/bkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001_01p.jpg&h=89eda297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【08:49】港鐵職員重啟幕門的系統搶修後，幕門運作恢復正常。港鐵宣布，港島線列車服務逐步回復正常。<br />\n<br />\n【08:15】受事故影響，港島線沿線月台迫滿人潮，有乘客不滿稱，今早上班一定遲到，鬧爆港鐵「次次都係咁，專揀繁忙時間先嚟故障。」其中姓歐陽乘客不滿港鐵只識加價，故障卻日日發生。<br />\n<br />\n【08:02】港鐵稱，堅尼地城往返柴灣列車改為3分鐘一班，整體行車時間有5至8分鐘延誤。<br />\n<br />\n【07:48】港鐵稱，港島線中環站月台幕門故障，工程人員已趕到現場搶修，港島線堅尼地城往返柴灣服務改為5分鐘一班，整體行車時間會有8至10分鐘的延誤，車站已加派人手協助乘客上落。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵中環站往柴灣方向3號月台，早上7時許，因全部幕門故障不能關上，所以港鐵需派出職員守在月台每一個幕門前，提醒乘客，以免因人多擠迫，有乘客不小心墮下路軌。而埋站列車全部需要慢駛，服務受阻。港鐵發言人稱，港島線中環站往柴灣方向，因月台幕門故障，列車出入月台需要行慢一些，服務會有延誤，請乘客為旅程預留充裕時間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171214/photo/bkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001_02b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001_02b.jpg&h=8efea804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n職員搶修月台幕門。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171214/photo/bkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001_03b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001_03b.jpg&h=9985bc47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中環站幕門故障，港鐵派職員在月台維持秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171214/photo/bkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001_04b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001_04b.jpg&h=fde4d18e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港島線沿線月台擠滿候車乘客。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171214/photo/bkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001_05b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001_05b.jpg&h=ea9fc5cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中環站幕門故障，列車慢駛離開月台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171214/photo/bkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001_08b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001_08b.jpg&h=1bd0229a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n月台擠滿候車乘客。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171214/bkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001.html?eventid=4028828d4f6e8e3f014f7ee0e6f470ae&amp;eventsection=hk_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171214%2Fbkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001.html%3Feventid%3D4028828d4f6e8e3f014f7ee0e6f470ae%26eventsection%3Dhk_news&d=oX%2FzVSq82eT82GbXMN2w9JUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=f4ffc4c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171214/bkn-20171214073202287-1214_00822_001.html?eventid=4028828d4f6e8e3f014f7ee0e6f470ae&amp;eventsection=hk_news</a>"},{"pid":"9999cef9b9ca1e14c659441269ce49c89e8269cf","tid":498675,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"港鐵壞幕門　乘客鬧爆：日日新鮮日日甘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171214/photo/bkn-20171214101200815-1214_00822_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171214101200815-1214_00822_001_01p.jpg&h=1509b1b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵港島線中環站幕門故障，由於正值早上上班繁忙時間，以致打工仔行程受阻。其中姓歐陽男乘客十分不滿，要求港鐵職員解釋事故原因，期間需要警員到場調解。歐陽不滿港鐵鬧爆稱：「呢間公司太過唔掂囉！」今日返工可能遲到10至15分鐘，出閘後「一定要跑返去公司。」<br />\n<br />\n他又埋怨港鐵次次在繁忙時間故障，他便先後遇過壞車及電力故障，「真係日日新鮮日日甘，半年壞十次以上&hellip;佢(港鐵)唔加價，我真要跪低多謝佢！」<br />\n<br />\n另外，一名從北角上車的女乘客指其行程受阻約20分鐘，幸她預早出門口，相信不會返工遲到。一名從柴灣上車的姓丘女乘客指，車程多了5分鐘，途經轉車站時，乘客比平時多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171214/bkn-20171214101200815-1214_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=4028828d4f6e8e3f014f7ee0e6f470ae\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171214%2Fbkn-20171214101200815-1214_00822_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dhk_news%26eventid%3D4028828d4f6e8e3f014f7ee0e6f470ae&d=oX%2FzVSq82eT82GbXMN2w9JUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=ac925977\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171214/bkn-20171214101200815-1214_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=4028828d4f6e8e3f014f7ee0e6f470ae</a>"},{"pid":"860736ffdb3b903df5be2cc94e6c93602ea836b3","tid":498675,"uid":10894,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:47:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2540517d4122a03564da4c9633da5091778cf55","tid":498675,"uid":60655,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我唔明 大條道理遲d 唔係應該幾開心咩<br />\n香港人真係好享受返工</blockquote><br />\n你係咪未出黎做過野<br />\n定你係太子仔"},{"pid":"f942ffc5e6d30f947c09e3476383d74a19295d3c","tid":498675,"uid":4519,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我唔明 大條道理遲d 唔係應該幾開心咩<br />\n香港人真係好享受返工</blockquote><br />\n你腦細都會大條道理屌鳩你唔早D出門口"},{"pid":"b227617ae6a68542dcd7653e0dd5c42e082030ae","tid":498675,"uid":12994,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實我唔明 大條道理遲d 唔係應該幾開心咩<br />\n香港人真係好享受返工</blockquote><br />\n你係咪未出黎做過野<br />\n定你係太子仔</blockquote><br />\n可能佢覺得有呢篇新聞就係免死金牌😂😂"},{"pid":"e78682cb62e8411235104cd0048fdd89a328dcd1","tid":498