\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e85ea7bfb933124e200f07b9b364c805fbf668","tid":498675,"uid":8557,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:19:39.000Z","msg":"歐陽先生呢招高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老闆而家知道啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803b43b7626a2a3f02dbb1b709c43a9bd1c99d83","tid":498675,"uid":129111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cospegmu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcospegmu&h=897e7c40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8c6ab1d20d0c6e476a2911d4e125cd0ea6cabb","tid":498675,"uid":96871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:31:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歐陽先生呢招高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老闆而家知道啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0960e8372b0debb1b6c65ae97c877bfdab4c5ed5","tid":498675,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:50:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d72772303a081f76eba33f4b03242b12d2c09b0f","tid":498675,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:29:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點解要慢駛？以前夠冇幕門啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中環站 3 號月台的月台門因故障而未能操作，車站職員已將之全部打開，讓乘客如常上落<br />\n<br />\n<strong>但月台門打開後期間會同時切斷行車訊號，列車需以不超過時速 22 公里進出月台範圍</strong>"},{"pid":"c1a502af97ce5d9dd846b9c4160799492d39bc49","tid":498675,"uid":48064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:46:09.000Z","msg":"屌你駛唔駛咁撚多黃衫友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}